# 🔐 MemoraAI Frontend Configuration
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Copy this file: cp .env.example .env.local
# Then replace all PLACEHOLDER values with your actual keys
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 🔑 REQUIRED KEY (Get from Google Cloud Console)
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Google OAuth2 - Client ID
# Get from: https://console.cloud.google.com/ → Credentials
# Format: 123456789-abc123xyz.apps.googleusercontent.com
# This is the SAME Client ID as in backend/.env
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=PASTE_YOUR_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID_HERE

# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 🔗 API CONFIGURATION
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Backend API URL
# Development: http://localhost:8000
# Production: https://yourdomain.com
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:8000

# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 📝 QUICK SETUP GUIDE
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# 1. Get Google Client ID:
#    Use the SAME Google Client ID from backend/.env
#    It's in GOOGLE_OAUTH_CLIENT_ID
#    Paste into: VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID
#
# 2. Verify Backend URL:
#    Make sure VITE_API_URL matches your backend location
#    Development: http://localhost:8000
#    Production: https://yourdomain.com
#
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
